---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: Episodes
permalink: /episodes/index.html
---

<h1>Episodes</h1>
<p>
  Episodes are named compound real-world happenings — protests, election days,
  congressional hearings, operations, court rulings with multiple defiance responses —
  that contain multiple recorded entries. Each episode page provides editorial overview
  of what the compound event was and lists every entry filed against it in chronological
  order.
</p>

{% if collections.episodes.length %}
  <ul class="episode-list">
    {% for episode in collections.episodes %}
      {% set episodeSlug = episode.data.slug or episode.fileSlug %}
      {% set entryCount = (collections.entriesByEpisode[episodeSlug] or []).length %}
      <li>
        <h2><a href="/episodes/{{ episodeSlug }}/">{{ episode.data.title }}</a></h2>
        <p class="episode-dates">
          <time>{{ episode.data.start_date | formatDate }}</time>
          {% if episode.data.end_date and episode.data.end_date != episode.data.start_date %}
            &ndash; <time>{{ episode.data.end_date | formatDate }}</time>
          {% endif %}
        </p>
        <p class="episode-counts">{{ entryCount }} entr{{ "y" if entryCount == 1 else "ies" }} documented.</p>
      </li>
    {% endfor %}
  </ul>
{% else %}
  <p><em>No episodes yet.</em></p>
{% endif %}
